game.name: Lemony Girls At Prom
game.description:
Hey ladies! The two most gorgeous women of this planet have got the invitation from the prom party tonight and lemon yellow is the prom theme. Wow! Does not it sound pretty exciting for your girls? Join Lemon Girls At Prom and be prepared to guide princess Elsa and Barbie to choose the perfect lemon yellow outfits combined with the matching accessories! The best part is that their wardrobe is full of yellow color dresses, cool handbags and sparkling jewelry pieces.

When you click the play button, you see the two girls having a conversation to mark their presence on the most awaited prom party. Start with Elsa by giving a yellow outfit in this brand new girls game! Dress her up with a fun with a plain yellow top or a top with some lemon prints or pair it with a cute red or a lemon printed skirt! Complete her look with a lemon-shaped handbag or lovely jewelry items! Now move on towards finalizing the look for Barbie in this HTML5 dressing game.

Apply your fashion abilities to help this cute doll to choose the jaw-dropping looks for the prom party! Give Barbie an elegant yellow top with a note at its bottom and pair with a lemon printed black skirt or a yellow full-length skirt! Choose a matching handbag and complete her look with a stylish hairstyle and an elegant piece of jewelry in this cute princess dress-up game! Try out new dress up games online here daily and have fun without download since we keep adding new fun girl titles to our website!
